{"tid":905744,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋知唔知你哋嘅父母喺點樣走埋一齊？","createTime":"2018-11-17T11:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T21:01:17.000Z","uid":91522,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef6fb7f0d5ddf2d08ec837032c141f26be2d41a","tid":905744,"uid":91522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"我啊爸啊媽一齊咗已經差唔多四十幾年<br />\n記得我媽咪話嗰陣娘家係開酒樓<br />\n細個嗰陣會落去幫我公公手賣點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n媽咪同我講 嗰陣有條花𡃁日日落去食燒賣撩佢講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我媽咪喺一個比較內向嘅人<br />\n但因為嗰陣佢好迷戀劉德華 又覺得呢條友有啲似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係咁樣比咗個機會我啊爸 最後一齊咗 直到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單而美好<br />\n你地又知唔知自己父母嘅愛情故事？<br />\n<br />\n利申 無我啊爸以前嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4cf95576c6f634e6e9e454c9ca8e3236edaa20","tid":905744,"uid":138138,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"證明女人都係睇樣"},{"pid":"3418a8538ccf0494bac40bf57b0776bfe2e32aa4","tid":905744,"uid":91522,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"bd4cf95576c6f634e6e9e454c9ca8e3236edaa20","tid":905744,"uid":138138,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"證明女人都係睇樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"大部份人都係睇樣先㗎啦 第一印象好重要係正常嘅事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdce89482085a37e07e625090bfe386b8b90c48","tid":905744,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"喺乜春呀"},{"pid":"4e52ce9e0ef7729f3f0f2ce49df3e7918047366a","tid":905744,"uid":138138,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3418a8538ccf0494bac40bf57b0776bfe2e32aa4","tid":905744,"uid":91522,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"bd4cf95576c6f634